  "strategy": [
    "Alternate between short forward moves and scans in exploration to maximize marker detection.",
    "Prioritize marker tracking and approach as soon as marker_seen is detected.",
    "On marker_lost during tracking, immediately initiate a scan to reacquire the marker.",
    "Handle all uncontrollable events in every state to ensure totality and safety.",
    "Use deterministic obstacle recovery: move backward from obs_front, rotate from obs_left/obs_right.",
    "Avoid oscillations by assigning only one rotation direction per side.",
    "After each forward commit or recovery, insert a scan to prevent long straight runs without perception.",
    "When marker_close is detected, transition to a terminal stop state to safely complete the task.",
    "Never allow move_forward from obs_front; always require a recovery step.",
    "Helper states ensure one-shot actions and clear transitions back to decision states."
  ]
